	<h1 class="title">医生现在可以这样出诊：  靠视频聊天进行快速诊断</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/463753/small/463753.jpg?1455020528" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Abba Goodnough</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-07-15 09:40:16 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/12054/medium/12054.jpg?1436854522" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="12054" data-title="《医生现在可以这样出诊：  靠视频聊天进行快速诊断》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/12054/medium/12054.jpg?1436854522" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/12054.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
